5. get a picture [For mjpg]
		

		*stop it by ctrl+c
		[root@Tiny4412 /]# ./luvcview -O -d /dev/video15 -f jpg
		luvcview version v0.2.4 
		video /dev/video15 
		Width = 320
		Height = 240
		Image size = 153600
		pixelformat = 1448695129
		get picture yuv...
		get picture !
		get picture yuv...
		get picture !
		get picture yuv...
		get picture !
		get picture yuv...
		get picture !
		get picture yuv...

		*There should be pictures with extension *pnm generated in ~/root_mkfs
			
		[For yuv]
		[root@Tiny4412 /]# ./luvcview -O -d /dev/video15 -f yuv


6.stream capture

		*capture video 
		[root@Tiny4412 /]# ./luvcview -S -d /dev/video15
		luvcview version v0.2.4 
		video /dev/video15 
		Width = 320
		Height = 240
		Image size = 153600
		pixelformat = 1448695129
		Starting raw stream capturing to stream.raw ...
			
		*stop it by ctrl+c and need a while to fully stop the capturing

		*There should be "stream.raw" stored in the same folder and play it with MPlayer
		
		[root@Tiny4412 /]# ./mplayer -vo fbdev -demuxer rawvideo -rawvideo w=320:h=240:format=yuy2 stream.raw -loop 0
		
		*Here we list the UVC webcam we have tried on this utility 			
		             ->logitech UVC Camera (046d:080f),UVC
		             ->sonix USB 2.0 Camera (0c45:6340),UVC
			     ->sonix USB 2.0 Camera (0c45:62f1),UVC <== (YUV only)	
